reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great customer service
reviews.reviewText: Ordered these, both are very long cords and work great. One of them stopped working due to it being damaged during shipping. I wasn’t sure how to reach out to the company to let them know but someone reached out asking how my product was? I let them know the issue they were quick to answer back and had a replacement sent out asap! The chargers work fast and the customer service is great.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The charging speed blows me away!
reviews.reviewText: I am absolutely blown away by quality of this iPhone. Not only does charge my phone incredibly fast, but also has a sleek and modern design that looks on my desk. The long charging cable gives the freedom to use phone while it's in, which is a huge. I have tried chargers in the past, but this one truly stands out as the best of the best. I will definitely be recommending this product to all of my friends and family.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Worked until it didn’t
reviews.reviewText: Loved these when they arrived. Now a month and a half later one has a short in it and will only charge when set at an angle. I keep it in the same place on my nightstand so it’s not being hassled. No reason it would have gotten shorted by handling. Purchase at your own discretionUpdate: Only days later after leaving this review did my charger completely stop working. It shows that my phone is charging but alas, after 8+ hours of being plugged in it has remained at 16%. Not worth the purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars XL cord but slow to charge
reviews.reviewText: I love love love the 10 meter cord. It's a game changer. If you've never tried using a phone charger with an XL cord, it's time to take the leap and change your life forever.The hardware itself is not Apple, which is obvious from looking at it. It isn't one of those super fast lighting chargers. But it does the job, it's durable, and like I said it's a super long cord!! 10/10 would buy again.Also of note: the connection between the cord and the brick is a USB-C port. So if you're traveling or you otherwise normally plug into a regular USB-A port, you won't be able to do that with this charger.
